vice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F13%2F155420_c5ab54ec2ebdc8d3a9a65e0427c8ff1b.png&h=5decf21b&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T07:55:11.000Z","msg":"爺爺個心好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T07:56:17.000Z","msg":"老人痴呆就退休啦<br />\n後備成堆後衛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4642358b7781fec18c8628ee6f4973b44147f93","tid":627439,"uid":48905,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T08:13:59.000Z","msg":"他知道哭是沒有用的"},{"pid":"1b908dec5e8fec72c553dca040162b9906737d93","tid":627439,"uid":157312,"like":9,"dislike":28,"score":-19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T08:37:10.000Z","msg":"「他知道，哭是沒有用的。」<br />\n<br />\n藍斯為父還債，所以17歲出道，開始了自己的演藝生涯。藍斯拍第一部片子《古惑仔》系列電影時，他和300多人打打殺殺，因為太過入戲，他不小心踢到了廢鋼鐵，腳立即受傷，血如泉湧。<br />\n<br />\n導演立刻喊停，要送他去醫院。他知道，這一去醫院，勢必要換人，那他的「星途」也許從此就斷了。於是，17歲的他對導演說：「找來300多人不容易，耽誤一天就是好多錢，我能堅持。」於是，他將酒精直接倒在傷口上，再將膠袋包著腳，穿上鞋子繼續拍攝。換了四個膠袋，倒出四袋血，戲拍完時，他幾乎暈倒。<br />\n<br />\n送到醫院，醫生說，再遲來一點，人就玩完了，而且，極有可能得到破傷風。在給他縫釘之前，醫生讓他簽生死狀。 在醫生給他縫釘時，藍斯就那麼看著，不喊、不叫、不哭，沒有打麻醉針，就那樣一釘一釘地縫著。一個17歲的少年，知道自己面對的是怎樣的人生。他知道，哭是沒有用的。<br />\n<br />\n最後一釘，藍斯對醫生說：「我來釘！」醫生看著他，他居然笑了︰「沒有嘗試過的人生，我都想嘗試一下。」<br />\n<br />\n這句話多麼豪邁，在場的人震驚了。因為醫生說，如果熬不過去，他也只有四天的生命了，所以，他願意嘗試生命中不曾嘗試的痛，他要給自己縫一針。<br />\n<br />\n從給自己縫針那一天開始，他知道，所有的明天全要靠自己。後來，他一直努力，不停地得獎，終於成為第三十屆足球先生。"},{"pid":"dcc3ed09eb236d331ad0963142f9d407d74ce3bd","tid":627439,"uid":82268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T08:40:44.000Z","msg":"忽肉撕開都咁都仲踢倒成場,真係痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a137a66e8cfd54a7a7371f03b141a6b65de3f3a","tid":627439,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"680a9981e5c2bec3206e172e26bbb4cb91dca8c0","tid":627439,"uid":54848,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T04:29:02.000Z","msg":"球壇林子健<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T08:41:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8817e45721b972bdb52c72461b120fa4e8e2dbe7","tid":627439,"uid":50740,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b7b0662078d45ffc41f769d38669da442ebecde8","tid":627439,"uid":7131,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"845be9585c969a3d766e8ca06b26b9e7c28ee4c5","tid":627439,"uid":4661,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T07:54:25.000Z","msg":"後備咁撚樣，斷腳都要踢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/13/155420_c5ab54ec2ebdc8d3a9a65e0427c8ff1b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F13%2F155420_c5ab54ec2ebdc8d3a9a65e0427c8ff1b.png&h=5decf21b&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T07:55:11.000Z","msg":"爺爺個心好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T08:43:46.000Z","msg":"kolasinac乜事英超歐霸一樣冇正選踢?"},{"pid":"1418189c17905d73fa0cc0c472bece73a2351594","tid":627439,"uid":58140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T08:45:06.000Z","msg":"好撚癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72381f71cfc9d8bc23046fe097fe5a9a7f3bb50e","tid":627439,"uid":62815,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T08:46:10.000Z","msg":"咁釘法個紋身會唔會崩左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f8948d5cb29bba5935c7b67ff6212b50e0104a1","tid":627439,"uid":21028,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1b908dec5e8fec72c553dca040162b9906737d93","tid":627439,"uid":157312,"like":9,"dislike":28,"score":-19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T08:37:10.000Z","msg":"「他知道，哭是沒有用的。」<br />\n<br />\n藍斯為父還債，所以17歲